Okay so i have been playing League for a little of 4 years i believe, I changed for a few months and went to Dota 2 (Till I realized that it will never compare to League) and i use to play offline bots on Dota a lot, this was just to practice so I could get better when I played online! I have recently been moving a lot as of late and haven&#039;t got adsl or any fancy internet, just simple ol phone 4g and I only get 4gb a month which is really sad! {{item:3070}} {{item:3070}} {{item:3070}} {{item:3070}} 
I understand this is a HUGE ask and that I am just one person, and it&#039;s probably the stupidest thing anyone has ever asked for but I can&#039;t only being able to play for 2 weeks and then have to wait another 2-3 to play again. I want to be able to keep practicing and getting to know my champs so when i do get more DATA I can dominate and maybe one day remove my account from bronze!{{item:3070}} {{item:3070}} 
BTW: Worlds Is Awesome and I will also be posting this on NA just to see if I can get others interested!
